features.description:
This is a Target variable. described as The total count of different doctors the patient has seen = {
 1: 0-1 doctors
 2: 2-3 doctors
 3: 4 or more doctors
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as The patient's age group = {
 1: 50-64
 2: 65-80
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as Whether stress affects the patient's ability to sleep = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as Whether medication impacts the patient's sleep = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as Whether physical pain disturbs the patient's sleep = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as Whether the need to use the bathroom affects the patient's sleep = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as Unidentified factors affecting the patient's sleep = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.

This is a Feature variable. described as General issues or difficulties the patient faces with sleeping = {
 0: No
 1: Yes
}
.
